node_7.subject: Maria Lopez
node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 9:00 am, have lunch at 12:00 pm, study at Hobbs Cafe from 1:00 to 3:00 pm, get at least 3 hours of gaming or streaming from 3:00 to 6:00 pm, go for a walk or jog at 7:00 pm, get back to Hobbs Cafe for dinner at 6:00 pm.
